a2t.text_actual: * Camera360 for Android v5.4.5 updated! *   **The Return of Sony Lens-style Camera and overall optimization.**   First choice free photo app for over 300 million users around the world! No.1 App in Photo & Video category in 75 countries, including US, Germany, Brazil, Spain, Russia, Korea, Singapore, Malaysia, India and China. Simply the most powerful and completely free photo shooting and editing app in the world. Camera360 has more than 200+ EXCLUSIVE FREE photo filters and multiple professional adjustment tools such as tilt-shift, overlay, texture etc. As your most professional mobile photography assistant, Camera360 is the ONLY app you will need to shoot, edit and share your photographs on the go. ##TOP FEATURES## # 10+ FREE CAMERA MODES (SELFIE CAMERA, FILTER CAMERA, SCENE CAMERA, FUNNY CAMERA, TILT-SHIFT CAMERA, AUDIO CAMERA, VIDEO AND MORE) # 200+ FREE EXCLUSIVE FILTERS # FREE LIMITLESS CLOUD ALBUM  # NEAR FIELD TRANSFER FOR INSTANT FREE PHOTO SHARING # INTELLIGENT FACIAL RECOGNITION AND BEAUTY SKIN SMOOTHING AND THINNING FEATURES # PROFESSIONAL PHOTO EDITING TOOLS # FAST EASY SHARING TO FACEBOOK, TWITTER, INSTAGRAM # ALL FREE, ZERO ADS!  [Feature Details]    1. New User Center  Find new blazing fast Near Field Transfer for instant free photo sharing here or in album! Manage all your messages in one place.   2. New Camera Store. ALL FREE!  10+ creative cameras in the“Camera Store” where you can add and manage your favorite camera modes. Different Camera modes including ID Photo Camera, Filter Effect Camera, Selfie Camera, Easy Camera, Scene Camera, Funny Camera, Tilt-shift Camera, Color-shift Camera, Audio Camera, Video Camera, all available for Free! Customize your own Camera360 now.  3. New Filter Effect Store. ALL FREE  200+ amazing exclusive filters are in the Effect Store where you can add and manage your own preferred filter effects. Paint your own night sky with the new splendid “Starry Night” filters!    4. User Friendly Photo Album  Photos are classified by date for easy photo searching and management. Photos in phone gallery can be browsed and edited in “Other Album”.   5. Professional Photo Editing UI and UX  Crop, Rotate, Blur, Texture, Adjust and more professional grade editing features are available.    6. Custom Ratio  Resize photo with ratio (16:9/4:3/1:1) while shooting.    7. Faster and better Cloud Service  Secure and smart cloud album for photo storage, management, editing, sharing and more. Support auto synchronization under uploading settings of Camera360 Cloud. Photos can be browsed on multi screens.   8. Photo Share  Photos can be shared easily via Facebook, Twitter, Flickr, Instagram, WeChat and more.
